Reason for revert: breaks downstream

Original change's description:
> [ObjC SDK]: Fix scalability mode not found error.
>
> Due to encoder factory not having properly advertised supported profiles and scalability modes, it was not possible to add a transceiver with an encoding with scalability mode provided.
